---
import Section from './Section.astro';
import Kicker from './Kicker.astro';
import BrandMark from './BrandMark.astro';
---
<Section id="story" tone="cream" spacing="xl" width="wide">
  <div class="grid gap-16 md:grid-cols-12 md:gap-20 items-start">
    <div class="md:col-span-5">
      <div class="reveal reveal--fade-up">
        <Kicker tone="coffee">Our Story</Kicker>
      </div>
      <h2 class="reveal reveal--fade-up mt-7 font-display text-display-lg text-forest text-balance" style="--reveal-delay:100ms;">
        Born from a love of the open road, the mountain, and the morning light.
      </h2>
      <div class="reveal reveal--fade mt-10" style="--reveal-delay:200ms;">
        <BrandMark size={64} tent="#603C0C" green="#186030" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="md:col-span-6 md:col-start-7 prose-editorial">
      <div class="reveal reveal--fade-up" style="--reveal-delay:150ms;">
        <p>
          Mtalii Bush Camps began with a shared vision of adventure. Inspired by a love for the open road,
          our founders journeyed to Nanyuki in a 4x4, seeking the freedom of the mountains. They were
          immediately captivated by the crisp air and the majestic presence of Mount Kenya.
        </p>
        <p>
          What started as a personal retreat evolved into a mission to share this magic with the world.
          Today, Mtalii Bush Camps is where adventure meets comfort — whether you are here for a challenging
          climb, a corporate retreat, or a peaceful escape, we invite you to start your next unforgettable
          chapter with us.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal reveal--fade-up mt-10 hairline" style="--reveal-delay:300ms;"></div>
      <p class="reveal reveal--fade-up mt-8 font-display italic text-2xl text-coffee text-balance" style="--reveal-delay:400ms;">
        “Strangers become friends, around the same fire, beneath the same mountain.”
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>
